videos.description: Kihei Clark finds Jack Salt open under the rim, who slams it to extend Virginia's early lead over Miami.
videos.headline: Salt gets open for the two-handed jam

videos.description: De'Andre Hunter blocks a defender at the rim and Kihei Clark flips it to Braxton Key on the other end for the score to put Virginia up by 10.
videos.headline: Hunter stuffs defender under rim, UVA scores on other end

videos.description: Virginia's Mamadi Diakite leaps up to stuff Miami's Sam Waardenburg shot underneath the rim.
videos.headline: Diakite gets up for vicious block under rim
